{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "92c7cf0d",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### #Using Ollama Embedding with Open-source models."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "id": "d492739c",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "| Parameter                             | Use                                                                |\n",
    "| ------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------ |\n",
    "| `base_url`                            | Hostname of Ollama server if not local                             |\n",
    "| `num_gpu`                             | Number of GPUs to use                                              |\n",
    "| `num_thread`                          | CPU threads                                                        |\n",
    "| `temperature`, `top_k`, `top_p`, etc. | Used more in generation models — usually not needed for embeddings |\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "id": "76137c1a",
   "metadata": {
    "vscode": {
     "languageId": "raw"
    }
   },
   "source": [
    "| Model               | Embedding Dimension                        |\n",
    "| ------------------- | ------------------------------------------ |\n",
    "| `mxbai-embed-large` | **1024**                                   |\n",
    "| `nomic-embed-text`  | **768**                                    |\n",
    "| `all-minilm`        | **384**                                    |\n",
    "| `embeddinggemma`    | **768**                                    |\n",
    "| `qwen3-embedding`   | Usually **1024** (depends on size variant) |\n",
    "| `granite-embedding` | Varies (commonly 768 or 1024)              |\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "🧠 Why Dimension Matters\n",
    "\n",
    "- Higher dimension → usually better semantic capacity\n",
    "- Lower dimension → faster search + smaller vector DB\n",
    "- Your vector DB index must match the embedding size"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "28aa02e9",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from langchain_ollama import OllamaEmbeddings"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "a239bb46",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "OllamaEmbeddings(model='mxbai-embed-large:latest', validate_model_on_init=False, base_url=None, client_kwargs={}, async_client_kwargs={}, sync_client_kwargs={}, mirostat=None, mirostat_eta=None, mirostat_tau=None, num_ctx=None, num_gpu=None, keep_alive=None, num_thread=None, repeat_last_n=None, repeat_penalty=None, temperature=None, stop=None, tfs_z=None, top_k=None, top_p=None)"
      ]
